data.name: tagValueGroupBox.ToolTip
data.value: The standard model ICP™ comes with a 60 GB solid-state drive capable of storing data up to 10 years without needing to resort to data destruction. This means you can easily find the last value of any tag, for any piece of equipment, at any point in time.

data.name: tagAggregateGroupBox.ToolTip
data.value: Aggregation rules can be enabled on the ProGauge ICP™ which will instruct it to build automatic summary information on an hourly and daily basis, to your specifications. If a point is so old that it no longer exists within the summary tables, you can still always retrieve it by performing a "Slow Scan".
